data.description: Discover this remarkable 3-bed, 3-bath ranch on a generous lot in the Wright City school district. Modern mix of wood and carpet floors throughout as well as a beautifully updated kitchen, spacious living room, and a stunning patio. The kitchen features quartz countertops and opens to the vaulted-ceiling living room with a cozy fireplace. Main floor master, walk in closets, vaulted kitchen and master bedroom, and LL wet bar. Recent upgrades include a new roof and HVAC system in 2021, newly poured driveway, stamped patio/sidewalk, and retaining wall with lighting add curb appeal and ensure modern comfort. You'll also appreciate the private backyard, perfect for outdoor entertaining, and the attached 2-car garage. Located in a quiet neighborhood with easy access to amenities, this home offers the ideal blend of comfort and convenience.
